OL,3,CMan stabbed in leg on Bank Holiday
OL,5,FA police investigation has been
OL,6,Flaunched after a man was stabbed in
OL,7,Fthe leg on Monday evening at Barry
OL,8,FIsland.
OL,10,FThe victim's injury is not believed to
OL,11,Fbe life threatening or life changing,
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police confirmed.
OL,14,FA police investigation is underway and
OL,15,Fenquiries are ongoing to trace the
OL,16,Fsuspect.
