OL,3,CMan stabbed in leg on Bank Holiday
OL,5,FInspector Lisa Gore: "Incidents such
OL,6,Fas this one are extremely rare and we
OL,7,Funderstand how distressing this
OL,8,Fincident was for those in the area at
OL,9,Fthe time.
OL,11,F"We have launched an investigation and
OL,12,Fa team of officers are carrying out
OL,13,Farrest enquiries for the suspect.
OL,15,F"We have further increase the police
OL,16,Fpresence in the area and this will
OL,17,Fcontinue over the coming days".
